    <Note Caller="1" LanguageCode="en" LastEdited="" LastEditedBy="">
      <References/>
      <Content>ἐπιστολή may occur either in the sense of the physical object (see {D:6.63}) which is used as a means of communication or as the content of what is written ({D:33.48}), but in some contexts it is difficult, if not impossible, to distinguish between these two phases of the meaning of ἐπιστολή.</Content>
    </Note>
